        "text": "While this model is leading a unit, add 1 to the Strength and Damage characteristics of this model\u2019s \u2019Eadbanger weapon for every 5 models in that unit (rounding down), but while that unit contains 10 or more models, that weapon has the [HAZARDOUS] ability.",
