        "text": "Once per turn, at the end of your Movement phase , one WEIRDBOY from your army can use this ability. If it does, roll one D6: on a 1, that WEIRDBOY \u2019s unit suffers D6 mortal wounds ; on a 2+, remove this WEIRDBOY \u2019s unit from the battlefield and set it up again anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 9\" horizontally away from all enemy models.",
